    "name": "Mechanines Tower Defense",
    "steam_appid": 3095890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/e077c3d3f87eb7bb7f3d31e751f6d7b1.apng?t=1739922536\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/e077c3d3f87eb7bb7f3d31e751f6d7b1.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=196 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mechanines Tower Defense</strong> 是一款结合了Rogue-lite元素与塔防动态的策略游戏，每场比赛都能带来独特的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与传统游戏不同，敌人的行进路径是程序化生成的，并且是无限的，确保每次游戏都不相同。此外，EvoDogs的放置点是随机的，这迫使玩家实时调整策略。 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略与耐力</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f45b3fc0f5481df338beedfad7adaf31.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f45b3fc0f5481df338beedfad7adaf31.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f45b3fc0f5481df338beedfad7adaf31.mp4?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场比赛都会带来新的挑战，随着你的进展，地图会不断扩展。成功的关键在于利用EvoDogs的独特能力，并借助程序生成的地形扩展来建立有效的防御。 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>位置与EvoDogs</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1da74dd31dbde9a4114c2f90f1dfbd5b.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1da74dd31dbde9a4114c2f90f1dfbd5b.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从各种类型的EvoDogs中选择，每个都有独特的能力，并将它们放置在战略位置，通过增加攻击力、耐力或战术支持来保护PetLab，从而影响它们的表现。 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DogCoins与技能</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1df411613e29794c99e084997abb9d44.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" width=800 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1df411613e29794c99e084997abb9d44.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1df411613e29794c99e084997abb9d44.mp4?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用DogCoins来进化你的EvoDogs，并解锁PetLab的永久升级，解锁新技能，并增强你的防御团队，以应对更难的机械敌人浪潮。 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全球竞争</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/28d719863d5b34b4999d6df3154ba6a2.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" width=800 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/28d719863d5b34b4999d6df3154ba6a2.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/28d719863d5b34b4999d6df3154ba6a2.mp4?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过全球或与好友竞争，挑战最高分，证明谁是最好的指挥官。准备好迎接一场史诗般的战斗，我们最忠诚和勇敢的朋友可以改变人类的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>胜利不是最重要的，永不放弃才是。</i></p>",
